headline: 3 Great Dividend Stocks to Buy Right Now for $33 or Less
summary: Several high-quality dividend stocks cost less than $33 a share.  Three great ones under that price point are Brookfield Renewable (NYSE: BEPC)(NYSE: BEP), Invitation Homes (NYSE: INVH), and Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI).
